## Web3Forms configuration
# Copy this file to `.env` (do NOT commit secrets) and set your key.
# Get an access key from https://web3forms.com
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your_web3forms_access_key_here

## Backend API configuration
# Local development example:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
# Production example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://vanguard-server-evr7.onrender.com/api
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
